<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd">
<html><head><meta name="qrichtext" content="1" /><style type="text/css">
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
</style></head><body style=" font-family:'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size:9.216pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-size:12pt;">autogen本地自定义函数</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;">https://microsoft.github.io/autogen/docs/topics/code-execution/user-defined-functions</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">exec()</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:medium; font-weight:600;">exec(skill.content, globals(), local_vars)</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-weight:600;">exec()</span><span style=" font-weight:600;"> 函数</span>：</li></ul>
<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 2;"><li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Python 内置函数 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">exec()</span> 用于动态地执行字符串形式的 Python 代码。它可以接受三个参数：</li></ul>
<ol style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 3;"><li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">代码字符串</span>：<span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">skill.content</span>，是需要执行的代码，这里是技能的代码内容（例如，一个函数定义）。</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">全局命名空间</span>：<span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">globals()</span>，提供全局变量的命名空间。</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-weight:600;">局部命名空间</span>：<span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">local_vars</span>，指定用于存储执行代码过程中创建的局部变量的字典。</li></ol>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">eval()</p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"># 定义全局变量</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;">x = 10</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"># 定义全局和局部命名空间</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;">globals_dict = {&quot;x&quot;: x}  # 将全局变量 x 放入全局字典</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;">locals_dict = {}         # 局部字典</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"># 使用 exec()，并指定 globals 和 locals</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;">exec(&quot;result = x + 5&quot;, globals_dict, locals_dict)</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"># 在 locals_dict 中可以访问到 result</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;">print(locals_dict['result'])  # 输出: 15</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">在 Python 中，</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">exec()</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 函数允许你通过 </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">globals</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 和 </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">locals</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 参数来指定全局和局部命名空间。这两个参数都应该是字典类型。下面是如何使用这两个参数的详细说明和示例。</span></p>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;">exec()</span><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;"> 的基本语法</span></h3>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">exec</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">(</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">object</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">, </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">globals</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">=</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#669955; background-color:#f3f3f3;">None</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">, </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">locals</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">=</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#669955; background-color:#f3f3f3;">None</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">)</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">object</span>: 要执行的代码字符串或代码对象。</li>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">globals</span>: 一个字典，指定全局命名空间。</li>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">locals</span>: 一个字典，指定局部命名空间。</li></ul>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">示例：指定</span><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;">globals</span><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;"> 和 </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;">locals</span></h3>
<h4 style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:medium; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">1. 使用共享作用域</span></h4>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 定义全局变量</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">x = 10</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 定义全局和局部命名空间</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">globals_dict = {</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">&quot;x&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">: x}  </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 将全局变量 x 放入全局字典</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">locals_dict = {}         </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 局部字典</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 使用 exec()，并指定 globals 和 locals</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">exec</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">(</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">&quot;result = x + 5&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">, globals_dict, locals_dict)</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 在 locals_dict 中可以访问到 result</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">print</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">(locals_dict[</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">'result'</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">])  </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 输出: 15</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<h4 style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:medium; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">2. 修改全局和局部变量</span></h4>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 定义全局变量</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">a = 5</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">globals_dict = {</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">&quot;a&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">: a}</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">locals_dict = {}</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 使用 exec() 来修改全局变量 a</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">exec</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">(</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">&quot;a += 10&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">, globals_dict, locals_dict)</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 检查 globals_dict 中的 a</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">print</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">(globals_dict[</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">'a'</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">])  </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 输出: 15</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">3. 使用</span><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;">locals</span><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000;"> 捕获局部变量</span></h3>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-weight:696; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">def</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; font-weight:696; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">my_function</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">():</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">    b = </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">3</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">    globals_dict = {}</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">    locals_dict = {}</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">    </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 使用 exec()，并指定 globals 和 locals</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">    </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">exec</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">(</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">&quot;c = b + 2&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">, globals_dict, locals_dict)</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">    </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># b 在 locals_dict 中</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">    </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#397300; background-color:#f3f3f3;">print</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">(locals_dict[</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#880000; background-color:#f3f3f3;">'c'</span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">])  </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"># 输出: 5  (b + 2 = 3 + 2)</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#697070; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;">my_function()</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Courier New'; color:#444444; background-color:#f3f3f3;"><br /></p>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">注意事项</span></h3>
<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">如果你在 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">exec()</span> 中尝试访问 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">locals_dict</span> 中的变量，它只在 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">locals_dict</span> 中可用，外部作用域无法直接访问。</li>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">使用 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">globals</span> 和 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">locals</span> 是一种强大的功能，但也要小心，因为它们可能会导致意外的行为，特别是在变量的命名冲突或作用域混淆时。</li>
<li style=" color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">尽量避免使用 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">exec()</span> 和 <span style=" font-family:'Courier New';">eval()</span>，因为它们可能导致安全问题和代码可读性差，尤其是当代码执行来自不可信的输入时。</li></ul>
<h3 style=" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" font-size:large; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">总结</span></h3>
<p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#f0f0f0;"><span style=" color:#000000; background-color:#f0f0f0;">通过指定</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">globals</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 和 </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">locals</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 参数，你可以控制 </span><span style=" font-family:'Courier New'; color:#000000;">exec()</span><span style=" color:#000000;"> 执行环境中的变量作用域和访问权限。这可以帮助你实现更灵活的代码执行，但同时也需要谨慎使用。</span></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"><br /></p></body></html>